ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectMinister of Citizenship and Immigration with Quebec and Manitoba - Resettlement Assistance Program - ** Agreement*
PrecisOrder Approving that the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration ENTER INTO CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS with QUEBEC AND MANITOBA with respect to the RESETTLEMENT ASSISTANCE PROGRAM, substantially in accordance with the a draft Agreement, in order to recognize the additional financial burden faced by these provinces in relation to irregular migration.
